title: VA - WTF compilation from gststracker

Due to the nature of the compilation, each of these discs contains a fair amount of bad language: only download if youre punk enough  

The first CD of this awesome collection is available here for you to download and savour....if you want the whole set, just rock over to gststracker.com and pick up the rest...you&#039;ll thank yourself for it! Hurry though, the site is going to become invite only very, very soon.
